Metadata: Washington's Efforts to Combat Invasive European Green Crab are at risk
For revised update see: WSG-AS 19-04 (WASHU-​G-​19-​006) similar but with different layout and emphasis (orange box)
Aggressive, adaptable and highly invasive, the Europeangreen crab has significantly impacted coastal ecosystemsworld​wide and now threatens the Salish Sea.
